{"type": "article", "id": 29560, "title": "一双鞋的进化革命, 让未来无可遁形#fluxit", "description": "新系列的立足点是什么？革命能否成功？", "date": "2016-07-18T15:30:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": 10, "author": 18, "comment_count": 13, "praise_count": 80, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607131616198L2ApBkCwZedYK6V.jpg", "contents": "<p>街头的少年们永不满足。他们身着中性的街头时尚运动装束，沉浸在数字世界，追逐新的智能技术，他们是狂热的社交媒体使用者，也是陈旧世界演变的催化剂。少年们怀揣好奇心，永远渴望领先一步，想在已知的世界里再创造出未知的一切，如同ZX FLUX ADV系列。</p><p>2014年，adidas Originals第一次推出ZX FLUX系列，以多彩印花激发无限想象。2016年7月，我们迎来进化升级版，以极简至型碰撞无限设计，创造了adidas Originals的鞋履传奇。全新 ZX FLUX ADV系列集中了adidas在运动装备上的技术，以其升级的流线型轮廓，摩登而简洁的设计，各种新面料的使用，完美集结三线记忆与摩登思维。向这个夏天宣告，创意永远不会停下脚步。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713161655vpg0tITCZsd3JoEP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.451384\" data-format=\"\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713161707jfgeZHsCP4iwYVxJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.703285\" data-format=\"\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713161713wo4UzYOJAqsR30Pl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.458333\" data-format=\"\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713161723ZYkDJRya3NQpuPbd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667183\" data-format=\"\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">服装：adidas Orignials;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">鞋：adidas Originals ZX FLUX</p></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">&nbsp; ZX FLUX ADV的创意深受上世纪70年代潮流影响。那是光荣与梦想的一代，是沉默的大多数向世界发出第一声呐喊的一刻，是民权暴动与热裤的兴起、是X级电影的风行，是离离原上草般的青年运动充斥街头——没人再想成为压抑的灰墙上的一块沉重的砖，人们努力地寻找自我，试图让自己的表达更富色彩。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713161746uoCbTctIQeOxh2UV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.441810\" data-format=\"\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713161759fil49ZO1YTPSkpcr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.767817\" data-format=\"\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713161811fEsuPdlHLArDOUCi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.253135\" data-format=\"\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607131618299wM2euEYjiID7vPQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667200\" data-format=\"\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;服装：adidas Orignials;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">鞋：adidas Originals ZX FLUX</p></figcaption></figure></div><p>ZX FLUX ADV 系列以“进化的革命”为主题打造而来：它强调不断变化的风格、新鲜的感受、冲锋在前端的现代性；乃至，融合未来科技，ZX FLUX ADV带来自由快感，更肆意地挥洒青春与创想。<br></p><p>今季新登场的ZX FLUX ADV Tech以网眼素材铸就而成，加入PU材质拼贴效果构成鞋身，配合创新鞋领塑造无限可能。女款ZX FLUX ADV VIRTUE则利用不规则鞋舌及鞋带演绎率性之美，TPU元素与鞋身上的三线标志是对FLUX系列的致敬，更延续了摩登简约格调。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607131619158bAGsZ1OIzQ5Bo2n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713161924RuZMhaVkiTULoGS7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713161951xahkFo1OjPwq0sCf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713162005ZjzpV67wdK5sPMcQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp; 鞋：adidas Originals ZX FLUX &nbsp;</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\">系列中的服饰同样以上述“进化的革命”为母题。男装方面深受到70 年代的潮流风范启发，长青迷彩图案大胆混合复古配色风格呈现；女装则着眼复古迪斯科风格，前卫线条轮廓，勾勒出昔日狂妄不羁的舞池文化。 &nbsp;<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713162046foJuAKUkTwdrIztF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713162056Pj78RDYVow3JGdHp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713162105nhc1N0xFrDyJOTmL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713162114gRSBQZqX5IUlen7E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;服装：adidas Orignials;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">鞋：adidas Originals ZX FLUX</p></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">塑造当代万变风格，未来无所遁形！ &nbsp;<br></p>"}